        "TileImage": "$($repository d0628b4d-98ac-4fc4-af51-a19eec39bc83).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, Agent. Welcome to Japan.\r\rYour target is Dr. Haruo Nakamoto; cosmetic surgeon and facial reconstruction specialist currently working out of GAMA Private Hospital in Hokkaido.\r\rDr. Nakamoto is best known for helping the ultra-rich express their &quot;inner beauty.&quot; However, the Target has also put his skills to good use creating dopplegangers — assassins and infultrators, replacers and influencers.\r\rWe are limited on time and options. Adapt quickly and exfil ASAP.\r\rGood luck, Agent.",
